```

#### 2. Always Jitter Mode
```
1. Enable "Always Jitter Mode" checkbox
2. Press Toggle Key → Macro ON
3. Hold LMB + RMB → Jitter pattern active
4. Release buttons → Jitter stops
5. Q key has no effect (locked to jitter)
```

